  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO PROVIDE THAT IF THE DEPARTMENT OF CORRECTIONS HAS ANY STATE INMATE IN A WORK ASSIGNMENT AND IN SUCH ASSIGNMENT THE INMATE UTILIZES RAW CLEANING CHEMICALS, THEN THE DEPARTMENT SHALL PROVIDE CERTAIN PROTECTIVE EQUIPMENT TO THE INMATE; TO AMEND SECTIONS 47-5-371, 47-5-401, 47-5-431, 47-5-441, 47-5-451, 47-5-453 AND 47-5-555, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO CONFORM TO THE PRECEDING SECTION; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
